My name is Dr. Charles Niwagaba
and I'm a senior lecturer of sewer

2
00:00:08,470 --> 00:00:13,043
engineering at Makerere University,
Kampala, Uganda.

3
00:00:13,243 --> 00:00:16,989
I have 16 years experience 
in sanitation.

4
00:00:17,189 --> 00:00:22,132
Now, faecal sludge management 
is a new and quickly evolving field.

5
